This is the 2001 release, a remastered version was released later in 2007.

One of the many celebrated release among Joe Purdy fans. Purdy introduces this album to the public with Isn't Love, a soft melodic song building up to a happier sound. As the earlier release, this album set the foundations for many albums to come..
